objects.description: [Duqu](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0014)s purpose is to \gather intelligence data and assets from entities such as industrial infrastructure and system manufacturers, amongst others not in the industrial sector, in order to more easily conduct a future attack against another third party.\ (Citation: Symantec)
